External knowledge needed to interpret this question correctly: 
1. Total interactions refer to the sum of comments and approvals made by a user; 
2. Time difference refers to the difference between the timestamps of the latest comment and the latest approval for each user; 
3. Approval rate is the proportion of approvals that have a status of 'approved'.

